### U - Approve/Reject Installation Form
### 1. Happy Path - Approve Installation Form (Status: true)
PATCH {{uri}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "empId": "6e9f757b-6fa1-4aa6-b7cb-a4cf2290eb20",
  "formNumber": "NUM-AHbUrpRI",
  "formCode": "FORM-b1a01c53-41d6-4881-a83e-61d9bb8564d2",
  "status": true
}

### 2. Happy Path - Reject Installation Form (Status: false)
PATCH {{uri}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "empId": "6e9f757b-6fa1-4aa6-b7cb-a4cf2290eb20",
  "formNumber": "NUM-AHbUrpRI",
  "formCode": "FORM-b1a01c53-41d6-4881-a83e-61d9bb8564d2",
  "status": false
}

### 3. Error Case - Missing Required Fields (Validation)
PATCH {{uri}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "empId": "6e9f757b-6fa1-4aa6-b7cb-a4cf2290eb20",
  "formNumber": "NUM-AHbUrpRI",
  "formCode": "FORM-b1a01c53-41d6-4881-a83e-61d9bb8564d2",
  "status": null
}

### 4. Error Case - Form Not Found (404)
PATCH {{uri}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "empId": "EMP-001",
  "formNumber": "NON-EXISTENT-NUM",
  "formCode": "NON-EXISTENT-CODE",
  "status": true
}

### 5. Error Case - Missing Authorization Header (401)
PATCH {{uri}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "empId": "EMP-001",
  "formNumber": "NUM-tVlgiCno",
  "formCode": "hehe1",
  "status": true
}

### L - Get Construction Orders List (đơn chờ thi công)
### 1. Happy Path - Get all construction orders (No param)
GET {{uri}}/construction
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 2. Happy Path - Pagination and Sort
GET {{uri}}/construction?page=0&size=10&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 3. Happy Path - Filtering by keyword, from, and to
GET {{uri}}/construction?keyword=Nguyễn&from=01-01-2024&to=31-12-2024
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 4. Error Case - Invalid Date Format (from)
GET {{uri}}/construction?from=2024-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 5. Error Case - Invalid Date Format (to)
GET {{uri}}/construction?to=01/01/2024
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 6. Error Case - Unauthorized (Missing Token)
GET {{uri}}/construction
